Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.47,0:00:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的纯真还真不像是个杀手啊 塔兹米
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个有趣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐这个比想像还有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.48,0:00:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不好
